    <h2>
      <a href="/episodes/137-memoization-revised">Memoization (revised)</a>
      
    </h2>
    <div class="description">
      Memoization is a convenient way to cache a method&#x27;s response.  Here I show several ways to accomplish this from scratch since the ActiveSupport::Memoizable module has been deprecated.
      <span class="stats">(9 minutes)</span>
    </div>
